summary: 20+ years of experience in structural engineering. Continuously working in the engineering field for Energy Sectors including (Oil and Gas, and Power), Industrial Sector, & Petrochemical Sector. Work experience in Netherlands, Germany, South Korea, KSA, and Egypt in onshore projects (Refineries, power, and hydrocarbons plants) and in offshore fixed platforms. Acquired experience in FEED, Basic, Detailed Design, and Rehabilitation projects. Former employers include tkIS, Samsung Engineering, WP, and Samsung C&T. Familiar with various industrial design codes.
